# Personalize Connect — Base Overview

**Purpose:** Zero-code bridge between Sitecore XM Cloud components and Sitecore Personalize Full Stack Interactive Experiences. Marketplace app configures; SDK handles runtime decisioning.

**Monorepo:**
- `packages/marketplace/` — Next.js 15 App Router app (port 5555), Blok UI, `/personalize-connect` route
- `packages/sdk/` — `PersonalizeProvider`, `withPersonalizeConnect`, `usePersonalizeExperience`

**Docs:** See `llms.txt` for full overview. Technical design: `docs/PERSONALIZE_CONNECT.md`. Blok: `packages/marketplace/BLOK.md`.
